const Home=({sp})=>(<>
<section style={{minHeight:"100vh",display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",justifyContent:"center",alignItems:"center",textAlign:"center",padding:"8rem 1.5rem 5rem",position:"relative"}}><div style={{position:"absolute",inset:0,background:"radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 20%,rgba(201,168,76,.06) 0%,transparent 70%)",pointerEvents:"none"}}/><div className="fade-in d1" style={{fontFamily:"var(--accent)",fontSize:"1.05rem",fontWeight:600,letterSpacing:".22em",textTransform:"uppercase",color:"var(--gold)",marginBottom:"2.5rem"}}><span style={{borderTop:"1px solid var(--gold-d)",borderBottom:"1px solid var(--gold-d)",padding:".5rem 0",display:"inline-block"}}>Your doctor found nothing. Your body disagrees.</span></div><h1 className="fade-in d2" style={{fontFamily:"var(--serif)",fontSize:"clamp(2.6rem,5.5vw,4.8rem)",fontWeight:900,lineHeight:1.1,color:"var(--cream)",maxWidth:900,marginBottom:"2rem"}}>"Everything Came Back <em style={{color:"var(--gold)",fontStyle:"italic"}}>Normal.</em>"</h1><p className="fade-in d3" style={{fontSize:"clamp(1.15rem,2vw,1.35rem)",color:"var(--muted)",maxWidth:640,lineHeight:1.8,marginBottom:"2.5rem"}}>I had 11 unexplained conditions. Every test was clear. Every specialist shrugged. Then I found the one thing they never thought to look for — and eliminated every symptom. Not managed. <strong style={{color:"var(--cream)"}}>Eliminated.</strong></p><div className="fade-in d4" style={{display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",alignItems:"center",gap:"1rem"}}><Btn large onClick={()=>sp(PG.TRAINING)}>Watch the Free Training</Btn><span style={{fontFamily:"var(--accent)",fontSize:"1.05rem",color:"var(--dim)"}}>30-min training + free book + free 15-min session</span></div></section>
<Sec><SL>If this is your life, keep reading</SL><Hd>You've been to the doctor. The bloodwork. The MRIs. The specialists. Same thing every time.</Hd><Bd>"We can't find anything wrong."</Bd><Bd>But the symptoms are still here. And the worst part isn't the pain — it's the feeling that <strong style={{color:"var(--cream)"}}>no one believes you.</strong></Bd><div style={{display:"grid",gridTemplateColumns:"1fr 1fr",gap:"1px",margin:"2.5rem 0",background:"rgba(201,168,76,.1)"}}>{["Chronic fatigue no rest can touch","Numbness or tingling, no cause","Panic attacks out of nowhere","Brain fog","IBS or stomach issues","Body twitching","Anxiety becoming agoraphobia","Widespread pain, no diagnosis","Insomnia despite exhaustion",'"Chronic Lyme" after antibiotics'].map((s,i)=><SI key={i} t={s}/>)}</div></Sec>
<Sec bg="var(--bg2)"><SL>What they missed</SL><Hd>Every symptom is a biological program — purposeful, specific, traceable to an exact moment.</Hd><CB t="The Off Note" d="Every conflict is sustained by a thinking error. Correct it, the biological program collapses."/><CB t="The Tracks" d="Your brain recorded everything when the shock occurred. Anything that rhymes with it reactivates the program."/><CB t="The Two Phases" d="You feel worst when life gets better — repair mode. The fatigue, inflammation, flare-ups? That's healing."/></Sec>
<Sec><div style={{textAlign:"center"}}><SL>My story. My proof.</SL><Hd>I carried 11 conditions. Eliminated every one.</Hd></div><div style={{maxWidth:560,margin:"0 auto 2rem"}}>{["Chronic Fatigue","Right Foot/Leg Numbness","Body Twitching","Panic Attacks","Agoraphobia","OCD","Bulimia (5 years)","Depression","High Blood Pressure","Chronic Lyme Symptoms","cPTSD"].map((c,i)=><RI key={i} c={c}/>)}</div></Sec>
<Sec bg="var(--bg2)"><SL>What others are saying</SL><Bridge/><TR items={[{id:"1181871159",h:"eb614a9a20",name:"Vernita"},{id:"1181871713",h:"34b14d1127",name:"Sylvia"},{id:"1181872201",h:"1d3bdb7e07",name:"Matt"}]}/></Sec>
<Sec><div style={{textAlign:"center"}}><SL>Free training</SL><Hd sz="clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)">Watch the Training. Get the Book. Book Your <em style={{color:"var(--gold)",fontStyle:"italic"}}>Free</em> Session.</Hd></div><div style={{maxWidth:580,margin:"2rem auto 0",padding:"2.5rem 2rem",background:"rgba(201,168,76,.03)",border:"1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.12)",textAlign:"center"}}><h3 style={{fontFamily:"var(--serif)",fontSize:"1.5rem",fontWeight:700,color:"var(--cream)",marginBottom:"1.2rem"}}>All free:</h3><div style={{textAlign:"left",marginBottom:"1.5rem"}}><FI t="30-minute training — the complete framework"/><FI t="The book — instant download — 'Everything Came Back Normal'"/><FI t="Free 15-minute session — your symptoms mapped, zero cost"/></div><Btn large onClick={()=>sp(PG.TRAINING)}>Get Instant Access</Btn></div></Sec>
<section style={{padding:"4rem 1.5rem",textAlign:"center",maxWidth:680,margin:"0 auto"}}><img src="https://i.imgur.com/M01AjHR.jpg" alt="Malcolm Kingley" style={{width:"100%",maxWidth:500,margin:"0 auto 2rem",display:"block",border:"1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.1)"}}/><p style={{fontFamily:"var(--serif)",fontSize:"clamp(1.3rem,2.5vw,1.65rem)",fontStyle:"italic",color:"var(--cream)",lineHeight:1.55}}>"Find the off note. Correct the thought. Watch the body follow."</p><p style={{fontFamily:"var(--accent)",fontSize:"1.1rem",color:"var(--gold-d)",marginTop:"1.5rem"}}>— Malcolm Kingley</p></section>
</>);

