const Library=({sp})=>(<><Sec pad="8rem 0 3rem"><SL>The Library</SL><Hd sz="clamp(2.2rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)">The Complete Works</Hd><Bd>Each book is a door into the framework. Every door leads to the same room.</Bd><Bd>These are not long reads. Every title is short, focused, and built around a single breakthrough — one concept, one shift, one correction. Most can be read in a single sitting. They are precision instruments, not textbooks. You read one, something clicks, and you move differently from that point forward.</Bd></Sec><Sec>{BOOKS.map(({cat,items})=>(<div key={cat}><p style={{fontFamily:"var(--accent)",fontSize:"1rem",fontWeight:600,letterSpacing:".22em",textTransform:"uppercase",color:"var(--gold-d)",marginBottom:"1.5rem"}}>── {cat} ──</p><div style={{display:"grid",gridTemplateColumns:"repeat(auto-fill,minmax(175px,1fr))",gap:"1rem",marginBottom:"3rem"}}>{items.map(b=><BC key={b.title} {...b}/>)}</div></div>))}</Sec><section style={{padding:"3rem 1.5rem",textAlign:"center",borderTop:"1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.08)"}}><p style={{fontFamily:"var(--serif)",fontSize:"1.25rem",fontStyle:"italic",color:"var(--cream-m)",marginBottom:"1.5rem"}}>Every book leads to the same door.</p><Btn large onClick={()=>sp(PG.BOOK)}>Book Your Free 15-Minute Session</Btn></section></>);

