<Sec><SL>Spiritual Special Warfare Operator School</SL><Hd sz="clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem)">Private Membership — By Invitation Only</Hd><Bd>The Operator School is the Kingley Foundation's proprietary training ground — where members learn to identify and correct thinking errors using Rawson's methods, Eddy's original first-edition work, the Five Mechanical Laws from the Codex, and the She-Wolf AI platform. In real time. Under pressure. When the Grid is screaming.</Bd><Bd>This is not a public offering. Our proprietary methods are reserved exclusively for accepted members.</Bd><div style={{margin:"2.5rem auto",maxWidth:600,textAlign:"center"}}><img src="https://i.imgur.com/ktGsAVB.jpg" alt="Operator School Hub" style={{width:"100%",border:"1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.12)",marginBottom:".8rem"}}/><p style={{fontFamily:"var(--accent)",fontSize:"1rem",color:"var(--dim)"}}>The Operator School — Members-Only Hub</p></div><div style={{maxWidth:520,margin:"2rem auto",padding:"2rem",background:"rgba(201,168,76,.03)",border:"1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.1)"}}><h3 style={{fontFamily:"var(--serif)",fontSize:"1.2rem",fontWeight:700,color:"var(--cream)",marginBottom:"1.2rem",textAlign:"center"}}>How to Be Accepted</h3><FI t="Complete a free 15-minute consultation with Malcolm"/><FI t="Receive a personal invitation to membership"/><FI t="Review and agree to the membership agreement"/><FI t="Membership is a paid commitment — not a free offering"/></div><div style={{textAlign:"center",marginTop:"2rem"}}><Btn large onClick={()=>sp(PG.BOOK)}>Book Your 15-Minute Consultation</Btn></div></Sec>

